326 HOSANNA BLESSED BE THE NAME

Hosanna, Blessed be the name, 
Blessed be the name of the Lord, 

Jehovah Jireh is His Name, 
Greatly He is to be praised ! 
Hosanna...

He is the Lord of lords and King, 
Shout His praises loud and Sing! 
Hosanna...




